Deciding whether to drink or not? Well look no further! Drinkology is here to solve your dilemma! Whether you're home alone and thinking about drinking a brewski or out with your friends at can't decide whose going to drink, this app will help you figure it out! Play single mode and see if you should have a sip or turn on party mode and put everyone's name in! Put a percentage and test your luck!



